      <item>
        <title>Version 2.4.14</title>
        <description><![CDATA[
          <h2>Functionality change</h2>
          <p>
            This version of QuoteFix changes the way customized attributions
            are handled.
          </p>
          <p>
            Before, customized attributions were seen as part of the
            quotefixing process, and if quotefixing was disabled, the
            customized attributions were disabled as well. With this version,
            customized attributions are separated from the quotefixing, so you
            can choose to disable quotefixing while still keeping the
            customized attributions.
          </p>
        ]]></description>
        <pubDate>Mon Nov  5 08:23:26 2012 CET</pubDate>
        <enclosure
          url="http://quotefixformac.googlecode.com/files/QuoteFix-2.4.14.zip"
